Comfort food isn't just for the weekend: this gnocchi and sausage bake with oozing mozzarella takes 30 minutes to make and can easily be made veggie by swapping in meat-free sausages. A pack of frozen chargrilled Mediterranean vegetables makes this recipe even easier, but you can use fresh if you don't mind a bit of chopping.
